profession for a few years.

00:05:42.090 --> 00:05:45.550
And I'm pretty privileged to
consider myself part of the

00:05:45.550 --> 00:05:49.230
larger worldwide conspiracy to
create the profession, or at

00:05:49.230 --> 00:05:51.090
least help support it.

00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:55.850
I think data science deserves
a new job title because it's

00:05:55.850 --> 00:05:58.370
not anything that we've never
been able to do before.

00:05:58.370 --> 00:06:02.110
