we've never combined into one

00:06:02.110 --> 00:06:03.780
professional before.

00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:07.610
And those three behaviors are
first, being able to do math

00:06:07.610 --> 00:06:11.280
and build models that represent
the real world.

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:14.220
The second one is being able to
write code or engineer the

00:06:14.220 --> 00:06:16.050
systems that support
those models.

00:06:16.050 --> 00:06:18.820
And sometimes to do it at
large scale as you guys

00:06:18.820 --> 00:06:22.370
certainly do and as we do
at a scale as well.

00:06:22.370 --> 00:06:26.100
And then third, to ask good
questions and be creative

00:06:26.100 --> 00:06:27.760
enough to communicate
what you've

00:06:27.760 --> 00:06:31.230
learned back to anybody.

00:06:31.230 --> 00:06:34.690
