available to everyone in the

00:19:16.840 --> 00:19:21.020
company, so that anyone can ask
a question and find that

00:19:21.020 --> 00:19:23.020
answer without having
to ask someone else.

00:19:23.020 --> 00:19:25.740
APRIL ANDERSON: That's great
