you did up there.

00:25:37.840 --> 00:25:40.360
And then let people tell
you why it's wrong.

00:25:40.360 --> 00:25:42.990
Because you will learn a lot,
and they will think it's cool.

00:25:42.990 --> 00:25:45.460
And you'll get a lot of good
feedback and start to meet

00:25:45.460 --> 00:25:49.350
